attributes.additional_details:
To be included in this petition:

Plastic wrapped vegetables and fruit; 
Single use plastic bags for purchasing fruit and vegetables (what happened to paper bags?)
Bubble wrap (sorry for those who like to pop the bubbles but the environment is more important); 
Clingfilm; 
Film lids from microwave meals; 
Non-recyclable crisp packets (metallic plastic); 

Next lets aim for abolishing single use water bottles and bring back water fountains - but that's for another day.
